rows.label: qst201607_msg0001
rows.name: ...I knew I couldn't do it.

rows.label: qst201607_msg0002
rows.name: Ah, is a shame, really...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0003
rows.name:
...I'm sorry I let you down.
I'll go get my stuff...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0004
rows.name: Uh? What friend saying?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0005
rows.name:
Even if perform on stage not go
so great, even standing on stage
in first place is great success!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0007
rows.name:
Song Nanakoori sing was cut short,
true, but it still touch people...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0008
rows.name:
Shy and sweet persona shine through
and pluck at heartstrings of audience!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0009
rows.name: ...Really?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0010
rows.name: Yes, really!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0011
rows.name:
If friend Nanakoori need proof, might be
interested to learn that her fan club
was established immediately!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0012
rows.name: ...That's...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0013
rows.name: Nice job, Nanakoori!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0014
rows.name:
It wasn't easy, but all's well
that ends well, eh?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0015
rows.name:
Nanakoori, what about that? Doesn't it
make you a bit happy at least?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0016
rows.name:
...I, uh...
Don't quite know what to think yet...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0017
rows.name:
Well, no. When everyone came just to
listen to me sing, that was kinda nice...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0018
rows.name:
That it!
That feeling very important!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0019
rows.name:
If manage to convey that feeling,
next concert will be sensational!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0020
rows.name: Convey...my feeling...to everyone...?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0021
rows.name:
Yes! We look to future, after all!
And with that, time for more lessons!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0022
rows.name: ...Yes! Okay!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0023
rows.name:
This time, we aim to improve
each area to level four!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0024
rows.name:
Build own potential, and confidence
surely follow! Teetapz think next time,
everything go swimmingly!
